title: Whale Recognition Model with score 0.78563
description: Whale Classification ModelThis notebook describes the strategy behind the 0.78563 submission to the Humpack Whale identification Challenge. It should be studied in conjunction with the Bounding Box Model notebook which describes separately the strategy for image cropping. To speed things up, the results of some slow computations are included as a dataset instead of being recomputed here. However, the code is still provided in the notebook as reference, even if it is not executed by default.
